1049
01:08:09.644 --> 01:08:13.227
(dramatic music continues)

1050
01:08:17.786 --> 01:08:21.369
(dramatic music continues)

1051
01:08:25.706 --> 01:08:29.289
(dramatic music continues)

1052
01:08:33.666 --> 01:08:37.249
(dramatic music continues)

1053
01:08:41.724 --> 01:08:43.195
(dramatic music continues)

1054
01:08:43.196 --> 01:08:46.279
(singers vocalizing)

1055
01:08:51.194 --> 01:08:55.027
